{"title":"Maven环境的安装","date":"2023-07-28T17:40:19.017Z","date_formatted":{"ll":"2023年7月28日","L":"2023/07/28","MM-DD":"07-28"},"link":"2023/07/28/Maven环境的安装","updated":"2023-07-28T08:49:12.714Z","content":"<h2 id=\"maven环境安装\">Maven环境安装<a title=\"#maven环境安装\" href=\"#maven环境安装\"></a></h2>\n<p>Maven环境的安装很简单，从网上下载Maven的压缩包，解压后，配置环境变量即可。</p>\n<p><strong>Maven连接Eclipse可以</strong><a href=\"https://blog.csdn.net/u014292402/article/details/105248141\" target=\"_blank\">参考这篇文章</a><br>\n<a href=\"https://blog.csdn.net/u014292402/article/details/105248141\" target=\"_blank\">https://blog.csdn.net/u014292402/article/details/105248141</a></p>\n<p><strong>1、下载Maven压缩包</strong><br>\n<img src=\"https://img-blog.csdnimg.cn/20200331110829272.png?x-oss-process=image/watermark,type_ZmFuZ3poZW5naGVpdGk,shadow_10,text_aHR0cHM6Ly9ibG9nLmNzZG4ubmV0L3UwMTQyOTI0MDI=,size_16,color_FFFFFF,t_70#pic_center\" alt=\"在这里插入图片描述\" loading=\"lazy\"></p>\n<p><strong>2、解压压缩包到你想安置的地方</strong><br>\n<img src=\"https://img-blog.csdnimg.cn/20200331111330501.png?x-oss-process=image/watermark,type_ZmFuZ3poZW5naGVpdGk,shadow_10,text_aHR0cHM6Ly9ibG9nLmNzZG4ubmV0L3UwMTQyOTI0MDI=,size_16,color_FFFFFF,t_70#pic_center\" alt=\"在这里插入图片描述\" loading=\"lazy\"><br>\n<strong>3、配置环境变量</strong><br>\n第一步：右击计算机<br>\n——&gt;选择属性<br>\n——&gt;高级系统设置<br>\n——&gt;高级<br>\n——&gt;环境变量<br>\n<img src=\"https://img-blog.csdnimg.cn/20200331111633850.png?x-oss-process=image/watermark,type_ZmFuZ3poZW5naGVpdGk,shadow_10,text_aHR0cHM6Ly9ibG9nLmNzZG4ubmV0L3UwMTQyOTI0MDI=,size_16,color_FFFFFF,t_70#pic_center\" alt=\"在这里插入图片描述\" loading=\"lazy\"><br>\n第二步：选择path<br>\n——&gt;点击编辑<br>\n——&gt;点击浏览<br>\n——&gt;选择到刚刚解压的目录<br>\n——&gt;点进去，选择bin目录<br>\n——&gt;点击确定<br>\n<img src=\"https://img-blog.csdnimg.cn/20200331112306388.png?x-oss-process=image/watermark,type_ZmFuZ3poZW5naGVpdGk,shadow_10,text_aHR0cHM6Ly9ibG9nLmNzZG4ubmV0L3UwMTQyOTI0MDI=,size_16,color_FFFFFF,t_70#pic_center\" alt=\"在这里插入图片描述\" loading=\"lazy\"><br>\n第三步：点击所有窗口的确定<br>\n<strong>4、确认Maven是否安装好</strong><br>\n快捷键win+r<br>\n——&gt;输入cmd，回车<br>\n——&gt;输入mvn  -v，回车<br>\n——&gt;显示如下结果，大功告成。<br>\n<img src=\"https://img-blog.csdnimg.cn/20200331112702487.png?x-oss-process=image/watermark,type_ZmFuZ3poZW5naGVpdGk,shadow_10,text_aHR0cHM6Ly9ibG9nLmNzZG4ubmV0L3UwMTQyOTI0MDI=,size_16,color_FFFFFF,t_70#pic_center\" alt=\"在这里插入图片描述\" loading=\"lazy\"><br>\n<img src=\"https://img-blog.csdnimg.cn/20200331112749620.png?x-oss-process=image/watermark,type_ZmFuZ3poZW5naGVpdGk,shadow_10,text_aHR0cHM6Ly9ibG9nLmNzZG4ubmV0L3UwMTQyOTI0MDI=,size_16,color_FFFFFF,t_70#pic_center\" alt=\"在这里插入图片描述\" loading=\"lazy\"></p>\n","prev":{"title":"nginx配置不生效","link":"2023/07/28/nginx配置不生效"},"next":{"title":"Maven连接Eclipse，发布第一个测试项目","link":"2023/07/28/Maven连接Eclipse，发布第一个测试项目"},"plink":"http://glj520.tk/2023/07/28/Maven环境的安装/","toc":[{"id":"maven环境安装","title":"Maven环境安装","index":"1"}],"reading_time":"358 字约 2 分钟"}